tipContents.cn: 队伍中干员装备强度较低，可通过<@gd.key>集成工业系统</>制造更好的装备。
tipContents.en: Equipped gear may be too weak. Use the <@gd.key>AIC Factory</> to make more powerful gear.

tipContents.cn: 队伍中干员等级低于推荐等级，可将干员进行升级和突破后再来挑战。
tipContents.en: Operator levels may be too low. Upgrade and promote them to make the challenge easier.

tipContents.cn: 队伍中干员等级低于推荐等级，可前往<@gd.key>协议空间</>获取干员经验与突破素材。
tipContents.en: Operator levels may be too low. Gather operator EXP and promotion materials from the <@gd.key>Protocol Space</>.

tipContents.cn: 队伍中干员技能等级低于推荐等级，可前往<@gd.key>天赋阵列</>进行技能升级。
tipContents.en: Operator skill levels may be too low. Go to the <@gd.key>Ability Matrix</> screen to upgrade their skills.

tipContents.cn: 队伍中武器等级低于推荐等级，可将武器进行升级和突破后再来挑战。
tipContents.en: Weapon levels may be too low. Upgrade and tune them to make the challenge easier.

tipContents.cn: 队伍中武器等级低于推荐等级，可前往<@gd.key>协议空间</>获取武器经验与突破素材。
tipContents.en: Weapon levels may be too low. Gather weapon EXP and tuning items from the <@gd.key>Protocol Space</>.
